CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

February 14, 2014

[Cite as 0211412014 Case Announcements, 2014-Ohio-514.]

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2013-1874. In re Application of Champaign Wind, L.L.C.

Power Siting Board, No. 12-160-EL-BGN. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Power Siting Board.

Upon consideration of the motion for leave to intervene as appellee of Champaign Wind, L.L.C., it is ordered by the court that the motion is granted.
